sub_title:
Ambitious, problem solver and great team leader, that is how people I know would describe me.
Out of the box mentality. 
"You can be a stripe and get in line or be a star and not be defined"
summary:
Young but goal-oriented, graduated at 21 in Palermo, Italy where I got my degree in interpreting and translation. With a background in languages I am currently looking for a job in the Netherlands in order to improve my dutch language skills gained during the last year. I am currently attending a Master's degree in Tourism Systems ad Hospitality Management 

Education taught me how work in a fast-paced environment, under pressure and respecting my deadlines. Excellent time management and problem solving skills and excellent leadership skills.

Foreing languages and culture lover. Passionate about music, food, baking, animals and most of all passionate about travelling.
